## Data Flow
```
Employee Login (TrayApp) → IPC → Service starts collectors
  → ActivityCollector captures keyboard/mouse counts every 150s
  → AppTracker polls foreground app every 5s, aggregates per interval
  → IdleDetector checks GetLastInputInfo
  → MeetingDetector scans for Teams/Zoom processes
  → DeviceTracker tracks active/idle sessions
  → All data → SQLite buffer
  → DataSyncService batches & POSTs to /api/v1/agent/ingest every 2-3 min
  → HeartbeatService POSTs to /api/v1/agent/heartbeat every 60s
  → PolicySyncService GETs /api/v1/agent/policy every 60 min
```
